{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"27388be3b0","title":"中共中央同意全国财贸书记会议商定的一九五九年夏季粮食和油菜籽征购计划","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0f815c1374","index":0,"year":1959,"month":5,"day":13,"articleId":"27388be3b0"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1893b82c61","type":"title","text":"中共中央同意全国财贸书记会议商定的一九五九年夏季粮食和油菜籽征购计划","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"10bdc39cac","type":"appellation","text":"各省、市、自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"0a88a9d93d","type":"paragraph","text":"中央同意全国财贸书记会议商定的一九五九年夏季粮食和油菜籽征购计划。除了有关征购工作的各项问题，另发指示以外，现在把分省征购计划转发各地执行。做好夏季粮食油料征购工作，对于保证秋粮登场以前的城乡粮食供应和油脂供应，对于保证今后一年中面粉供应和粮食品种的调剂，具有重要意义。请你们抓紧时机，及早布置，坚决保证夏季征购任务的圆满完成。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"172927989d","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央一九五九年五月十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"8bb102e7a1","type":"paragraph","text":"附发：（一）一九五九年夏季粮食征购计划","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"44d12080f8","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）一九五九年夏季油菜籽征购计划","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"45351787e3","type":"appellation","text":"中央：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"634f4376fd","type":"paragraph","text":"在最近召开的全国财贸书记会议上，经过讨论，议定了一九五九年夏季粮食（小麦、早稻、杂粮）和油菜籽的征购计划。这个计划所规定的各地征购指标，已经通过到会同志，分别征得了各省、市、自治区党委的同意，现在把分省的征购计划送上，请中央审查，转发各地执行。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"5235bf84d2","type":"paragraph","text":"附带说明，这次所提出的征购计划，是今年夏季征购粮食和油料的计划；至于全年的粮食征购指标，仍然按照上海会议所确定的一千一百五十五亿斤不变。中央对各省、市、自治区粮食油料的管理，也仍然按照上海会议确定的购销差额，由地方包干不变。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"a2df448a47","type":"paragraph","text":" 李先念一九五九年五月五日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"b88b78a47f","type":"subtitle","text":"一九五九年夏粮征购计划","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"3b64c2522c","type":"paragraph","text":"做好今年的夏季粮食征购工作，及时掌握粮源，是缓和当前粮食供应紧张情况的一个十分重要的方面，对于下一个年度粮食局势的稳定，也有直接的影响。因此，在今年夏粮收获以后，必须根据瞻前顾后，以丰补歉，细水长流，计划用粮的原则，在做好农村粮食分配工作的基础上，及早地尽可能地多收一些夏粮，以保证秋粮上市以前城乡的粮食供应和出口的需要。现在分别将小麦、早稻和夏熟杂粮的征购计划说明如下：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"baaf105ff5","type":"subtitle","text":"一、小麦","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"2ab0665e0a","type":"paragraph","text":"今年计划征购小麦二百二十亿斤，比上年度实际征购的一百七十亿斤增加五十亿斤。过去几年小麦的商品率是：一九五六年百分之二十九点九三，一九五七年百分之三十点三八，一九五八年百分之二十二点七，一九五八年小麦商品率之所以较低，是因为农村留量放宽的结果，一九五九年小麦产量比一九五八年实产量七百四十八亿斤，肯定会有增加，今年国家征购二百二十亿斤，商品率不会超过以往几年。因此，今年征购二百二十亿斤的计划应当保证完成，并且力争超过一点。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"6e0ab51cbf","type":"paragraph","text":"在小麦供应方面，按照从紧掌握的精神，每月供应小麦十五亿斤，全年是一百八十亿斤。今年在秋收以前，还须要拿出二十亿斤小麦代替大米和杂粮的供应，再加上出口十亿斤，军粮五亿斤，全年共须支出小麦二百一十五亿斤。这样，小麦收支相抵仅余五亿斤。显然仍然是一个比较紧张的局面。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"5e8516482b","type":"paragraph","text":"小麦是全年粮食收获中的一部分，过去征购当中一般是留下种子和接上秋粮以前大约三个月的口粮。按照这个办法估算，全国小麦主要产区有农民三亿人，在接秋早的地方每人约留口粮八九十斤，接秋晚的地方每人留口粮一百一二十斤，三个月平均以每人留一百斤计算，共留三百亿斤。一九五九年小麦播种面积以五亿亩计算，每亩留种三十斤，共留一百五十亿斤。两项合计，农村留四百五十亿斤。这样，完成国家征购计划二百二十亿斤以后，农村仍然会有不少小麦。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"45d3d390d6","type":"subtitle","text":"二、早稻","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"673eb868fa","type":"paragraph","text":"早稻是指七、八月份能够征购的稻谷。计划今年征购一百二十二点五亿斤（折合大米数，下同）。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"3a5fcde89b","type":"appellation","text":"“以早济晚”不仅靠小麦，还必须抓早稻。今年由于国家库存大米减少太多，更有必要及早多抓。早稻主要产区，过去几年七、八月份（广东包括六月份）的征购量是：一九五六年六十六亿斤，一九五七年八十九亿斤，一九五八年九十亿斤。今年征购一百二十二点五亿斤是必要的，也是可以收得到的。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"a794bb0f2b","type":"subtitle","text":"三、夏季杂粮","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"0d4dfbfcc2","type":"paragraph","text":"夏季杂粮，主要是指大麦、元麦、蚕豆、豌豆和南方早玉米。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"b8ce41d4e3","type":"paragraph","text":"计划今年征购二十八亿斤，同一九五八年征购量相等。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"d88a609c43","type":"appellation","text":"夏季杂粮不仅在当地供应有一定作用，也是大城市副食和出口方面所必需的，特别是蚕豆、豌豆和作为啤酒原料的大麦。过去在收购季节，有些地方对这些品种往往不加注意，收购不好，以致全年供应困难。接受过去的经验教训，今年应该注意抓一下。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"0c6f4de5a8","type":"subtitle","text":"一九五九年夏粮征购计划","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"9173fd63e0","type":"appellation","text":"单位：亿斤","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"651ac3ffce","type":"appellation","text":"地  区\t小麦（包括春麦）\t早稻（折合大米数）\t夏杂粮（大麦、元麦、蚕豆、豌豆）\t附注","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"28a9c02897","type":"appellation","text":"全  国\t220.00\t122.50\t28.00","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"afb4fbe58c","type":"appellation","text":"北  京\t0.80","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"8826eac5a1","type":"appellation","text":"上  海\t0.70\t\t0.30","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"bb8aef2e1e","type":"appellation","text":"河  北\t15.00\t\t1.50\t包括天津","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"a1fa4ecf6f","type":"appellation","text":"山  西\t9.00\t\t0.30","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"b719f024b8","type":"appellation","text":"内  蒙\t7.20","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"11f8e60380","type":"appellation","text":"辽  宁\t0.20","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"e535c9e7f0","type":"appellation","text":"吉  林\t0.80","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"41343970a2","type":"appellation","text":"黑龙江\t10.00","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"dc8e38f311","type":"appellation","text":"陕  西\t14.00\t\t0.50","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"76abb8af24","type":"appellation","text":"甘  肃\t11.50\t\t0.10","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"45339ffa18","type":"appellation","text":"宁  夏\t3.00","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"6479600782","type":"appellation","text":"青  海\t2.60","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"57a635f0fa","type":"appellation","text":"新  疆\t10.00","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"b5b1d3630b","type":"appellation","text":"山  东\t25.00\t\t1.00","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"060f2bb282","type":"appellation","text":"江  苏\t10.00\t3.00\t4.00","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"fbdd0d141c","type":"appellation","text":"安  徽\t20.00\t8.00\t4.00","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"93787c63cb","type":"appellation","text":"浙  江\t2.00\t16.00\t3.00","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"90e6086aae","type":"appellation","text":"福  建\t0.30\t6.00\t0.20","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"1139cc21b1","type":"appellation","text":"河  南\t40.00\t\t3.00","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"6797216603","type":"appellation","text":"湖  北\t10.00\t6.00\t3.00","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"08831c553a","type":"appellation","text":"湖  南\t1.50\t14.00\t0.30","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"e9544be15c","type":"appellation","text":"江  西\t0.50\t15.00\t0.30","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"480b30d60c","type":"appellation","text":"广  东\t0.20\t25.00\t0.10","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"8d4737509f","type":"appellation","text":"广  西\t0.20\t5.50\t0.80","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"924a92cef0","type":"appellation","text":"四  川\t20.00\t24.00\t4.00","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"5cdd06dd3a","type":"appellation","text":"贵  州\t4.00\t\t0.10","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"ae3adef2af","type":"appellation","text":"云  南\t1.50\t\t1.50","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"04329599c3","type":"subtitle","text":"一九五九年夏季油菜籽征购计划","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"fd267d6c3e","type":"paragraph","text":"目前油脂情况很紧张。四月二十日全国库存只有九点九亿斤，比去年同期减少二点六二亿斤。城市库存十分薄弱，许多小城镇和农村已经脱销，出口计划完成很差，拖欠很多，工业用油也很紧张。从现在起到秋季油料收获还有六个月。在这个期间，主要是依靠油菜籽的征购来保证出口和维持国内的供应。因此，对夏季油菜籽不能不狠狠地抓一把。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"e86dd4a7f9","type":"appellation","text":"一九五九年夏季油菜籽的播种面积比一九五八年增加了几百万亩。目前生长情况一般良好，产量将会比去年增加不少。我们建议一九五九年征购夏季油菜籽二十点二亿斤是不多的。以往各年夏季油菜籽的商品率：一九五六年是百分之七十九点五，一九五七年是百分之八十，一九五八年是百分之五十九。一九五八年夏季油菜籽的商品率之所以降低，是因为农村留油多了，国家征购少了。今年要求全国商品率达到百分之八十以上。在全部油菜籽由国家征购、农村用油由国家供应的地区（这种地区在全国占大多数），商品率要求提高到百分之九十；在采取农村留油办法不用国家再行供应的地区，农村留油的数量也应当从紧掌握，以保证完成国家的征购计划。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"f6bccb1145","type":"subtitle","text":"一九五九年夏收菜籽主要产区征购计划","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"3a7cc9d2e4","type":"appellation","text":"单位：亿斤","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"247dbfe454","type":"appellation","text":"地区\t收购计划","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"f83dbecf36","type":"appellation","text":"12个省市合计\t20.20","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"c4bb49c3f2","type":"appellation","text":"上海\t1.00","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"cd6a0e1cb7","type":"appellation","text":"陕西\t0.30","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"d5e099c3b3","type":"appellation","text":"江苏\t1.00","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"9b529baf29","type":"appellation","text":"安徽\t1.80","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"c64d2a2da6","type":"appellation","text":"浙江\t2.30","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"40c108aff0","type":"appellation","text":"湖北\t2.80","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"4091b05d6c","type":"appellation","text":"湖南\t0.50","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"d0ffac3b80","type":"appellation","text":"江西\t1.00","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"2eb09a64d0","type":"appellation","text":"广东\t0.20","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"f35d094461","type":"appellation","text":"四川\t7.00","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"56a73870b4","type":"appellation","text":"贵州\t1.50","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"},{"id":"89140de8f0","type":"appellation","text":"云南\t0.80","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0"}],"page":{"id":"db9273eb8c","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"27388be3b0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}